Impeccable timing, Your Majesty.

45
00:05:18,110 --> 00:05:20,950
Why, if it isn't my big brother...

46
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:24,420
descending from on high to mingle with the commoners.

47
00:05:24,450 --> 00:05:27,550
