48
00:05:27,590 --> 00:05:29,680
That was today?

49
00:05:29,730 --> 00:05:32,990
Oh, I feel simply awful!

50
00:05:33,130 --> 00:05:35,330
Must've slipped my mind.

51
00:05:35,370 --> 00:05:38,560
Yes, well, as slippery as your mind is...

52
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,730
as the king's brother...

53
00:05:39,770 --> 00:05:42,500
you should've been first in line!

54
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:44,560
Well, I was first in line...

55
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:46,580
until the little hairball was born.

56
00:05:46,610 --> 00:05:49,410
That hairball is my son...

57
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:51,610
and your future king.

58
00:05:51,650 --> 00:05:54,450
Oh, I shall practice my curtsy.

59
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:57,080
Don't turn your back on me, Scar.

60
