Bad back, you know.

157
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:02,180
Hey, Uncle Scar, when I'm king, what'll that make you?

158
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:04,410
A monkey's uncle.

159
00:12:04,450 --> 00:12:06,180
You're so weird.

160
