166
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:23,360
And he's absolutely right. It's far too dangerous.

167
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:25,890
Only the bravest lions go there.

168
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:28,700
Well, I'm brave. What's out there?

169
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:30,930
I'm sorry, Simba, I just can't tell you.

170
00:12:30,970 --> 00:12:32,170
