174
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:42,340
All the more reason for me to be protective.

175
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:46,680
An elephant graveyard is no place for a young prince.

176
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:49,210
An elephant what? Whoa.

177
