Oh, dear, I've said too much.

178
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:55,420
Well, I suppose you'd have found out sooner or later...

179
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:58,400
you being so clever and all.

180
00:12:58,430 --> 00:13:00,160
Oh, just do me one favor.

181
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:04,870
Promise me you'll never visit that dreadful place.

182
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:08,070
- No problem. - There's a good lad.

183
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:10,910
You run along now and have fun.

184
00:13:10,950 --> 00:13:14,940
And remember, it's our little secret.

185
