188
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,660
And it's time for yours.

189
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,330
Mom!

190
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:35,000
Mom, you're messing up my mane!

191
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:37,870
OK, I'm clean. Can we go now?

192
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:40,900
So, where are we going? It better not be anyplace dumb.

193
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:42,780
No, it's really cool.

194
00:13:42,810 --> 00:13:45,410
So, where is this really cool place?

195
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:48,350
Oh. Around the water hole.

196
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:51,480
