- All right! - Yeah!

204
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,140
As long as Zazu goes with you.

205
00:14:06,170 --> 00:14:08,200
No, not Zazu.

206
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:11,140
Step lively. The sooner we get to the water hole...

207
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:13,300
the sooner we can leave.

208
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:15,280
So, where are we really going?

209
00:14:15,310 --> 00:14:17,840
- An elephant graveyard. - Wow!

210
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,610
Shh! Zazu.

211
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:22,380
Right. So how are we gonna ditch the dodo?

212
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:25,390
Oh, just look at you two.

213
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:28,620
Little seeds of romance blossoming in the savanna.

214
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:30,920
Your parents will be thrilled...

215
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,330
what with your being betrothed and all.

216
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:36,230
- Be... what? - Betrothed. Intended.

217
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:38,200
Affianced.

218
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,360
